episodes.synopsis: When water meets land, species like dolphins, monitor lizards, baboons, and even lions must use special hunting skills to survive.
episodes.title: Exposed

episodes.synopsis: Visit places of vast openness where predators like Mongolian wolves and African cheetahs must hide in plain sight to hunt dinner.
episodes.title: Naked

episodes.synopsis: In the tropical forest canopy and spongy moss floor, unique predators such as glass frogs rely on stealth-like skills to survive.
episodes.title: Stealth

episodes.synopsis: Dive beneath the icy waves of Alaska's Aleutian Islands to see the incredible and surprising hunting and feeding techniques of killer whales.
episodes.title: Wet

video.title: Secret Life of Predators
video.synopsis: Explore the world of predators and learn how, whether large or small, fierce or stealthy, they all have individualized skills to help them survive.
